The paper discusses the use of computer vision and machine learning techniques for processing histopathologic images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also covers unsupervised learning (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques, which are commonly used in image processing. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep learning methods (cs.MM) for image classification.
